  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large bowl, mix together olive oil, onion, carrots, zucchini, red bell pepper, and fennel seeds.",
    "Spread the mixture evenly on a baking sheet and roast for 25 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add grapes and continue roasting for another 15 minutes, or until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Stir in honey, lemon juice, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Garnish with chopped fines herbes and serve hot.",
    "Serve with crusty bread or couscous, if desired."
